    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">The recursive nature of the Backrooms can also be seen in the various pathways and routes that connect different sections of the maze. As a person traverses the space, they may find themselves entering a room they have already been in, or they may stumble upon a new path that leads them deeper into the maze.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
